Why did my ad fail to pass review?

Ad rejection reasons can vary, such as incorrect conversion tracking setup or typographical errors. You should receive an email from Ad Support with the specific reason for your ad's rejection. I recommend checking that email carefully and addressing the highlighted issue. For more details, you can refer to our article on what to do next after an ad gets rejected: [My ad got rejected. What's next?](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18085960681101-My-ad-got-rejected-What-s-next). If you believe your ad complies with the policies or if the rejection was a misunderstanding, you can submit an appeal by emailing adsupport@newsbreak.com.
